PrecisOrder prescribing an additional period during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to the Hon. JACQUES J. LEVESQUE, a Puisne Judge of the Superior Court of Quebec (District of Trois-Rivières), who was required to relocate from the Town of La Tuque to the City of Trois-Rivières.
